siteMetadata.title: Norman and OKC Personal Protective Equipment Squad
siteMetadata.description: Join Norman and OKC volunteers in donating 3D Printed PPE.

node.excerpt: How can I help? Donation of materials we need. We currently need: PETG (preferred) or PLA, 1.75 mm, no “add-ins” like glitter or similar. Unopened packages preferred. 0.5 mm to 1.0mm PETG clear plastic sheets at least 16x10 inches. Other types can be…
